name: Almost sente comic strip book
description: The game of go. Wei-ki, baduk... why should be so serious? Here is the funniest book about go you would ever read! Meet two opponents, who need nothing but goban and stones to get THE nirvana! They will reanimate dead shapes with a drip, hang stones on the Christmas tree and use an axe to break the ladder! The greatest gift you can hand to your go-mad mate, the most wired award in the history of your local tournaments! Get your copy now, but remember: order more than one at once: you'll want to give them to all your friends from the club!
